<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Jaymani Krishi Sewa - Farmer Feedback</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: #f6f6f6;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: auto;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  h1 {
    text-align: center;
    color: #2c3e50;
  }
  p {
    text-align: center;
    color: #555;
  }
  label {
    display: block;
    margin: 15px 0 5px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  input[type="text"],
  input[type="tel"],
  textarea,
  select {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  input[type="checkbox"], input[type="radio"] {
    margin-right: 10px;
  }
  .option-group {
    margin-top: 5px;
  }
  button {
    background-color: #27ae60;
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 25px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 6px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }
  button:hover {
    background-color: #219150;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
  <h1>Jaymani Krishi Sewa - Farmer Feedback</h1>
  <p>This survey is conducted by Manish Pandey and Jayant Raj from Sharda University to understand challenges faced by farmers in rural agriculture.</p>

  <form id="farmerForm">
    <!-- Section 1: Farmer Info -->
    <label for="name">Full Name *</label>
    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>

    <label for="village">Village</label>
    <input type="text" id="village" name="village">

    <label for="mobile">Mobile Number</label>
    <input type="tel" id="mobile" name="mobile">

    <label for="crops">Crops Grown</label>
    <input type="text" id="crops" name="crops" placeholder="e.g., Wheat, Rice">

    <!-- Section 2: Problem Identification -->
    <label>1. Market Distance</label>
    <div class="option-group">
      <input type="radio" name="market_distance" value="0-5 km" required> 0–5 km<br>
      <input type="radio" name="market_distance" value="5-10 km"> 5–10 km<br>
      <input type="radio" name="market_distance" value="10 km+"> More than 10 km
    </div>

    <label>2. Stock Issues</label>
    <div class="option-group">
      <input type="radio" name="stock_issue" value="Frequently" required> Frequently<br>
      <input type="radio" name="stock_issue" value="Sometimes"> Sometimes<br>
      <input type="radio" name="stock_issue" value="No"> No
    </div>

    <label>3. Resource Loss (Time/Money)</label>
    <input type="text" name="resource_loss" placeholder="e.g., ₹100, 2 hours">

    <label>4. Pricing Transparency</label>
    <div class="option-group">
      <input type="radio" name="pricing" value="Yes" required> Yes<br>
      <input type="radio" name="pricing" value="No"> No<br>
      <input type="radio" name="pricing" value="Unsure"> Unsure
    </div>

    <label>5. Current Practice</label>
    <div class="option-group">
      <input type="checkbox" name="practice" value="Phone Calls"> Phone calls<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="practice" value="Word of Mouth"> Word of mouth<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="practice" value="Direct Visit"> Direct visit to market<br>
      <input type="checkbox" name="practice" value="Other"> Other
    </div>

    <label>6. Prefer SMS for stock info if no internet?</label>
    <div class="option-group">
      <input type="radio" name="sms_access" value="Yes" required> Yes<br>
      <input type="radio" name="sms_access" value="No"> No<br>
      <input type="radio" name="sms_access" value="Maybe"> Maybe
    </div>

    <label>7. Advance Reservation of stock?</label>
    <div class="option-group">
      <input type="radio" name="advance_reserve" value="Yes" required> Yes<br>
      <input type="radio" name="advance_reserve" value="No"> No
    </div>

    <label>8. Connect digitally with verified local shops?</label>
    <div class="option-group">
      <input type="radio" name="local_shops" value="Yes" required> Yes<br>
      <input type="radio" name="local_shops" value="No"> No
    </div>

    <label>9. Suggestions (Optional)</label>
    <textarea name="suggestions" rows="4" placeholder="Your suggestions..."></textarea>

    <label>10. Willingness to use Jaymani Krishi Sewa?</label>
    <div class="option-group">
      <input type="radio" name="willingness" value="Yes, definitely" required> Yes, definitely<br>
      <input type="radio" name="willingness" value="Maybe, if easy"> Maybe, if it is easy<br>
      <input type="radio" name="willingness" value="No"> No
    </div>

    <button type="submit">Submit Feedback</button>
  </form>
</div>

<script>
  document.getElementById("farmerForm").addEventListener("submit", function(e){
    e.preventDefault();
    alert("Thank you for your feedback! Form submitted successfully.");
    this.reset();
  });
</script>

</body>
</html>
